version_description:
- Search for content, people, and channels. The Search icon has taken the place of the Featured tab in the main navigation bar.
- Featured has moved to the Home tab as a feed filter. Home now includes 3 tabs for My Feed, Featured, & Trending.
- Deep-linked push notifications to Articles now take you directly to the full Article body so you can start reading a post right away.
- You can now navigate to another userâ€™s private profile, but you will only be able to see their name & avatar.
